data.description: $10,000 PRICE REDUCTION + $5,000 PAINT ALLOWANCE!  Discover serenity in this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence nestled in the picturesque Eagle Springs community. Positioned along the tranquil community pond, this home offers a retreat-like atmosphere, perfect for unwinding after a long day. Enjoy added peace of mind with NEW major systems including a 1 year old roof, 2 year old HVAC and 3 year old water heater! The main level features a charming living area with a fireplace, creating an inviting space for cozy evenings. The well-appointed kitchen boasts a dining area and abundant cabinetry for practical storage solutions. The Owner's Suite, conveniently located on the main level, is a haven of luxury, featuring a private bathroom with a jetted tub, tile shower, double vanity, and a spacious walk-in closet. Ascend to the second level to find three additional bedrooms, sharing a jack-and-jill style bathroom. Beyond the confines of this elegant abode, revel in the benefits of residing in a gated neighborhood with a plethora of amenities. From the community pool with a waterslide to the gym area, clubhouse, tennis courts, playground and more, every day presents an opportunity for recreation and relaxation in this vibrant and secure enclave. Don't miss out on this precious home.  Call today to schedule your private showing.
